channel.title: I'M STUMPED! Question about making my webclient
channel.description:
Hey guys, im new here but I'm working on making my first webclient. I am using Ric's Webclient Tutorial - located here: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=336494.0
I've gotten to the part in Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1 where I have to change where the client finds the sprites (atleast I think thats what I'm doing). It says to search in that file for ./Sprites/ and replace it with C:/.yourclientname_file_store_32/Sprites/, but I cannot find anything named ./Sprites/...
If someone could PLEASE help me, Id really appreciate it! I am using a DELTA source.
THANKS!
